28:29.075 --> 28:31.241
- I'll meet you
back here, okay?

28:31.243 --> 28:34.044
Back here.

28:34.046 --> 28:37.214
- Dad?

28:37.216 --> 28:39.183
What are you doing here?

28:50.361 --> 28:52.930
- Get a lot
of writing done today?

28:55.366 --> 28:58.135
- Come here.
Come here.

28:58.137 --> 28:59.803
- What's wrong?
- Come here.

28:59.805 --> 29:01.472
- What's the matter?
What?

29:12.484 --> 29:15.119
