Were you worried?
- No.

31:28.287 --> 31:31.655
- Did I scare you?
- Oh, shit, I have to go.

31:31.657 --> 31:34.491
- What, you got somewhere
to be at 10 to 5:00?

31:36.961 --> 31:38.629
- Yeah.

31:49.374 --> 31:51.241
Will?

31:58.917 --> 32:01.451
Hey.
