34:39.277 --> 34:42.279
[horse neighs]

34:44.849 --> 34:46.750
- Martin.

34:49.087 --> 34:50.353
Martin.

34:58.429 --> 35:00.630
- Ah, shit.

35:02.700 --> 35:06.603
I just wanted to help
with the new horse, I swear.

35:06.605 --> 35:09.306
Please don't tell
my parents.

35:16.214 --> 35:18.715
- Martin, I got
to ask you something,

35:18.717 --> 35:21.284
