35:38.203 --> 35:39.469
- You can take my work,
little man.

35:39.471 --> 35:40.737
- More?
- Yeah.

35:40.739 --> 35:42.472
- Would you like
some more juice, sweetie?

35:42.474 --> 35:44.774
- Yeah.
- Martin, my man.

35:44.776 --> 35:46.643
- Oh, hey, buddy.
- Hi.

35:46.645 --> 35:49.546
- Now, martin, it is wonderful
