36:25.684 --> 36:27.450
You will never guess
who I ran into.

36:27.452 --> 36:29.186
That little redhead
who was in your class

36:29.188 --> 36:32.389
The year that dad died,
that had a crush on hal.

36:37.261 --> 36:40.263
[phone ringing]

36:45.603 --> 36:47.837
- Hello?

36:47.839 --> 36:50.874
Mrs. Solloway?

36:50.876 --> 36:55.312
