just noticed he's gone?

37:41.927 --> 37:45.662
- She has four children.

37:45.664 --> 37:48.398
- Yeah, well, so what?

37:48.400 --> 37:51.334
- So she might have a bit
on her mind.

37:51.336 --> 37:53.003
- No, she doesn't.

37:53.005 --> 37:55.405
