39:27.466 --> 39:28.965
- What?

39:28.967 --> 39:32.102
- After you left
the hotel.

39:32.104 --> 39:33.103
- Why?

39:33.105 --> 39:35.505
- You left so quickly,

39:35.507 --> 39:38.708
